.com/uravenofmemory.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ravenofmemory</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(7/23/01 4:47:55 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm26.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=249.topic&index=21>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Polykarbon Roleplaying, Chapter 1</span><hr size=1> Ed looked concernedly at Liz, and took a sip from his coffee. &quot;Visions...haven't heard about anything like that for a long time. Of course, the ghosts I c'n sympathize with...my house is kinda badly haunted, if I do say so myself. Pretty embarassing to have an 18th-century woman walk in on you in the shower, lemme tell ya...&quot;<br>
