&quot;theres someone else in here..&quot;she whispered to herself. <br>
Liz thought of a hasty excuse,&quot;uh um..excuse me..i'm going to go look for the bathroom,&quot; Liz scurried around the corner than stopped. She knew what the room he was hiding in looked like,she just needed to find out where. she walked slowly down the hall and stopped in front of the last door. <br>
&quot;um..you don't have to hide in there..none of us care about what you did,in fact,only i know. And ya know,a guy with a gun hiding in a dark corner isn't exactly comforting,&quot;Liz put on the best smile she could muster. In truth she was scared out of her wits. Well ALMOST.<br>
&quot;so...will you come out?&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#aaaaaa><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/uwinlabik.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Winlabik</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(7/26/01 10:01:00 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm26.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=249.topic&index=36>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Polykarbon Roleplaying, Chapter 1</span><hr size=1> ((I've got to go for 10 days, be back on the 31st.  Gothic, I'm giving you control of my character <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  )) <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/uwinlabik.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Winlabik</A> at: 7/26/01 10:01:15 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/usempaisloan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>SempaiSloan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(7/26/01 12:50:50 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm26.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=249.topic&index=37>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Polykarbon Roleplaying, Chapter 1</span><hr size=1> &quot;so...will you come out?&quot; <br>
<br>
A tingling rush filtered through Deuce's trunk... that half-resigned half panic of getting caught. On a typical job, that meant he was dead, or he'd have to kill someone. But not today.<br>
<br>
She was just too curious. And she sounded scared.<br>
<br>
Deuce pulled his hand out of his coat, and let it rest in clear sight near his thigh. He inched out from the shadows behind the door, and stepped into the hallway. He tried to keep his gameface on, but it failed him when her eyes met his. She was piercing.<br>
<br>
He took a breath, and forced the best grin he could muster. &quot;Feel better, now?&quot;<br>
<br>
She just stood there watching him, her eyes fluttering back and forth between his.<br>
<br>
&quot;You've got sharp ears. I didn't think I gave myself away.&quot;<br>
<br>
A conversation continued in the room beyond her, and Deuce dropped his voice.<br>
<br>
&quot;You seem to think you know me. I don't think you do. Even if you did, what would that change? Not this storm! If you were a cop, you'd have arrested me. If you were a Fed, you wouldn't be alone. If you belonged to Velario...&quot; He chuckled. &quot;...you would have just shot me.&quot;<br>
<br>
Her shoulders were relaxing a little.<br>
<br>
&quot;If you're going to be afraid of anything out here, it's not me.&quot; Deuce looked back at the windows of the office. &quot;But what's up there? @#%$. With that many friendlies tearing ass up the coast... who knows what's going on in Alaska? Hell, maybe we're at war.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#aaaaaa><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/ubeige.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Beige</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(7/26/01 1:12:05 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm26.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=249.topic&index=38>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.livejournal.com/userpic/67453 WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Polykarbon Roleplaying, Chapter 1</span><hr size=1> The awkward silence caused by the woman's abrupt exit continued. Vick, Ross, and the other man continued to stare at each other warily under the furniture.<br>
<br>
&quot;This is stupid.&quot; Vick climbed out from under the desk and stood up. I'm Vick Paterno, and the cowering joke of an agent you see under that desk over there is Ross Powell.&quot; Vick paused, sniffed the air, and wandered off to find coffee.<br>
<br>
&quot;We're with the FBI field office in Seattle. Been searching around for a witness to a criminal case... appears to have flown the coop on us.&quot; Ross added helpfully. The man's only response was an extremely dubious look. He stood up, and began to introduce himself. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/ugothicchaos.showPublicProfile?language=EN>gothic chaos</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(7/26/01 1:55:05 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm26.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=249.topic&index=39>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Polykarbon Roleplaying, Chapter 1</span><hr size=1> Liz broke her gaze from Deuce's<br>
&quot;i didn't hear you,i saw you,&quot;<br>
Liz chewed on her bottom lip for a moment before she spoke,&quot;who's Velario?I've never heard of him,does he work for the goverment?&quot; Her eyes glanced at the windows.<br>
&quot;those things,the ones that are making so much noise,they're UFOs. I don't know what they're doing,but i don't think they're attacking, yet,&quot; Liz thought for a moment.<br>
&quot;and....i don't really know you,but i do know why your here. Why you've been acting so mysterious and why you have that gun,&quot;She looked back up at Deuce and smiled.<br>
&quot;hey,mabey you can help us,the more the merrier,ya know?&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#aaaaaa><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/usempaisloan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>SempaiSloan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(7/27/01 4:38:28 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm26.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=249.topic&index=40>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Polykarbon Roleplaying, Chapter 1</span><hr size=1> &quot;UFO. You too, huh?&quot; He turned a shoulder to her, and stole a glance out the windows again. Another rumble shook beneath his feet.<br>
<br>
The very fact the Deuce was alive was a miracle. He'd found himself at the business end of too many maniac's barrels to make any more assumptions about anything. That's how he survived... by never allowing prejudice to cloud his options.<br>
<br>
But this was going a little further than he was willing to go.<br>
<br>
However, there were two people, now, who were convinced that those... things... hurling through the sky were unearthly. One MUFON hipster, and this... extraordinary woman. And there was something about her perception.<br>
<br>
&quot;So, I guess this means you're a psychic, or something?&quot; He shook his head. &quot;I don't suppose it matters.&quot;<br>
<br>
Deuce leaned against the wall. Twelve years growing up in San Diego. He'd learned what military aircraft sounded like. But... he had to admit, that was a long time ago. And those craft were flying through winds that would beat the hell out of a Tomcat.<br>
<br>
He released a heavy sigh. &quot;Well, if those really ARE UFO's, then I'm going to need a bigger gun.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm26.showMessageRange?topicID=249.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b> <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm26.showMessageRange?topicID=249.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a><a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm26.showMessageRange?topicID=249.topic&start=61&stop=80>4</a><a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm26.showMessageRange?topicID=249.topic&start=81&stop=92>5</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm26.showPrevMessage?topicID=249.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm26.showNextMessage?topicID=249.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm26.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=249.topic&index=40><img src=http://www.polykarbon.com/bbsimage/addreply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm26.emailToFriend?topicID=249.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm26.threadControl?topicID=249.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm26.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=249.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm26.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=249.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of rep